quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  23,33,"Maze ibikomerezwa byo mu bantu be bahakanye (Allah) bakanahinyura kuzahura n’umunsi w’imperuka, kandi twarabahaye ubuzima bwiza hano ku isi, biravuga biti “Uyu nta cyo ari cyo usibye kuba ari umuntu nkamwe, urya ibyo murya akananywa ibyo munywa.”"
  23,34,"Kandi nimuramuka mwumviye umuntu nkamwe, mu by’ukuri muzaba mubaye abanyagihombo"
  23,35,Ese abasezeranya ko nimuramuka mupfuye mugahinduka igitaka ndetse n’amagufa (akabora) muzazurwa
  23,36,"Ibyo musezeranywa (na Hudu) biri kure, kure cyane"
  23,37,"Nta bundi (buzima buzabaho), usibye ubu buzima bwacu bwo ku isi! Turapfa, tukanabaho (hakaza abandi) kandi ntabwo tuzazurwa"
  23,38,"(Hudu) nta cyo ari cyo, usibye kuba ari umuntu uhimbira Allah ibinyoma, kandi ntabwo tuzamwemera"
  23,39,(Hudu) aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Ntabara unkize (abantu banjye) kubera ko bahakana (ibyo mvuga).”
  23,40,(Allah) aravuga ati “Rwose mu kanya gato baraba bicuza (impamvu bahakanye).”
  23,41,"Maze urusaku rw’ibihano rubatera rutabarenganyije, nuko tubahindura nk’ibishingwe (bireremba hejuru y’amazi). Bityo, kurimbuka nikube ku bahakanyi"
  23,42,Nuko nyuma yabo turema ibindi bisekuru
  23,43,Nta bantu bashobora kwihutisha igihe cyabo (cyo kurimbuka) cyangwa ngo bagikerereze
  23,44,"Hanyuma twohereza intumwa zacu zigenda zikurikirana, ariko buri uko intumwa yageraga mu bantu bayo (yatumweho) barayihinyuraga. Nuko tugenda tubakurikiza (ibihano) bamwe ku bandi, kandi tubagira iciro ry’imigani (kugira ngo bizabere isomo n’inyigisho ku bazabaho nyuma). Bityo, kurimbuka nikube ku bantu batemera"
  23,45,"Hanyuma twohereza Musa n’umuvandimwe we Haruna, tubahaye ibitangaza byacu n’ibimenyetso bigaragara"
  23,46,"(Tubohereza) kwa Farawo n’ibyegera bye, ariko (barabasuzugura) bagaragaza ubwibone, kandi bari abantu bishyira hejuru"
  23,47,"Baravuga bati “Ese twemere abantu babiri bameze nkatwe, kandi bene wabo ari abacakara bacu?”"
  23,48,"Nuko babahinyura bombi, maze (Farawo n’ibyegera bye) baba mu boretswe"
  23,49,Kandi rwose twahaye Musa igitabo (Tawurati) kugira ngo bayoboke
  23,50,"Twanagize mwene Mariyamu (Issa) na nyina, ikimenyetso (kigaragaza ubushobozi bwacu), nuko tubatuza ahirengeye, hatekanye kandi hari amazi"